  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00542', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設市場上有兩家廠商在生產口罩，其平均成本與邊際成本皆固定為 AC=MC=10，市場需求則 為Q=q1+q2=100-P。下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["若依照Cournot數量競爭模型，兩間廠商將會在對手產量固定的假設下選擇極大化利潤", "若依照Cournot數量競爭模型，則市場總產量為60", "若依照Stackelberg數量競爭模型，領導廠商將會在觀察追隨廠商反應函數後選擇極大化利潤", "若依照Stackelberg數量競爭模型，則市場總產量為57.5"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00543', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於薪資收入（earnings）的敘述，何者正確？', '["薪資收入指的是經常性薪資", "薪資收入提高代表勞工生產力的提高", "實質薪資收入提高代表勞工購買力的提升", "一國平均實質薪資收入會隨著時間提高"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00544', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '強烈颱風吹倒全國一半的香蕉樹，在勞動僱用量不變下，會導致在香蕉園工作農民的：', '["勞動邊際產出上升", "勞動邊際產出下降", "勞動邊際產值上升", "勞動邊際產值下降"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00545', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設在勞動市場中共有100家廠商，每一家個別廠商都有相同的勞動需求曲線L=100-W，其中L 為勞動需求量而W為工資。則此勞動市場整體的勞動需求函數為何？', '["L=100-W", "100L=100-W", "L=10000-100W", "L=100-100W"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
